snippet.title: Chopped Celeb
snippet.description:
Providing you with self-made & high- quality content to keep you up-to-date in the celebrity world and show you their best and worst moments with a little twist.

Here is some insight into my video creation process: I spend hours upon hours every day researching new topics that I could potentially make fun & entertaining videos on. After I'm satisfied with my video's topic, I get into the scripting. This can take anywhere from 30min to 3 hours, depending on how complex the video is. Once I am done with the script, I record the audio and make sure that the quality is perfect for you guys. 

All my videos are edited with Adobe Premiere Pro and the whole editing process can take me anywhere from 3-5 hours per video. Overall, this is probably the most time-consuming part.

Schedule: Currently, I post videos every Monday, Wednesday, Friday, and Saturday of every week at exactly 11am EST.

I hope to see you in my videos! :) 

For Business Inquiries please contact the email address below 👇
